   --!a:[*[&GraphicOld_id]:character_id]|InspireByName: ** |InspireByTID: **
   --&BardicFlag|0
   --<|
  
  --:AnswerNo|
  --<|
  
  --:Crit|
   --#whisper|
   --+Save: |[*[&GraphicOld_id]:character_name] rolled a [$Save] vs a DC [$DC] and cannot fail the saving throw. 
   --+|[br]
   --+Result: |[*[&GraphicOld_id]:character_name] is still concentrating.
   --X|
  
  --:Success|
   --+Save: |[*[&GraphicOld_id]:character_name] rolled a [$Save] vs a DC [$DC] and passed the saving throw. 
   --+|[br]
   --+Result: |[*[&GraphicOld_id]:character_name] is still concentrating.
   --X|
   
  --:Fail|
   --+Save: |[*[&GraphicOld_id]:character_name] rolled a [$Save] vs a DC [$DC] and failed the saving throw. 
   --:DeadEntry|
   --+|[br]
   --+Result: |[*[&GraphicOld_id]:character_name] lost concentration.
   
   --C[&SpellTokenName]|Bane:>Bane|Banishment:>Banishment|Bless:>Bless|Divine Favor:>Favor|Faerie Fire:>Faerie|Greater Invisibility:>Invisibility|Guidance:>Guidance|Hex:>Hex|Hold Person:>Hold
