   --%loop|foreach;tokens
	--~|object;token;delete;[*[&loop]:t-id]
	--%|
   
   -->LibSN_REMOVE_STATUS_MARKER|[*[&GraphicOld_id]:t-id];[&ConcentrationMarker]
   --!a:[*[&GraphicOld_id]:character_id]|ConcentrationSpell:**
